{"tid":764350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人聽朝想一齊睇戲 - <AV女優的告白>(不喜慎入)","createTime":"2018-08-02T01:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T13:58:11.000Z","uid":197796,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"780dee5a3245d93cf075475ce995234a88442cee","tid":764350,"uid":197796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:47:43.000Z","msg":"小弟三十出頭，德國工作回流返黎冇耐(⚠️注意⚠️唔係獨宅)<br />\n<br />\n咁啱聽朝放假冇嘢做想睇個戲，發覺身邊正常嘅朋友，都冇乜興趣陪我睇呢啲重口味少少嘅題材，所以就黎連登發個文，睇吓有冇人有興趣啦，順便識下新嘅朋友仔咁囉 .... (不過最好係女㗎啦，如果唔係就好似兩個麻甩仔約埋去睇AV咁 .... 😅)<br />\n<br />\nAnyway ，有興趣嘅就留個言啦 (第一次發文，唔知連登有冇得PM嘅呢🤔) <br />\n<br />\n3/8 朝早11:05，油麻地百老匯電影中心，坐H6、H7好冇呢？希望到時會見到妳/你啦~ (想有下文，會唔會諗多左啦🤣)<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/094721_e228e63882f3c52d9821617ffee42400.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F094721_e228e63882f3c52d9821617ffee42400.png&h=cc9452e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/094723_45f85108e1cf384e9c42d0112b89b7a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F094723_45f85108e1cf384e9c42d0112b89b7a9.png&h=aba0096b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34f3d0120363b16291ad4f2ced9adda5c52fc54b","tid":764350,"uid":154554,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"點解一定要搵人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f3a0b3edb39331999269f7369122fa2a77b006","tid":764350,"uid":197796,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"34f3d0120363b16291ad4f2ced9adda5c52fc54b","tid":764350,"uid":154554,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"點解一定要搵人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:53:56.000Z","msg":"其實冇人陪我都會自己去，不過順便睇下會唔會咁都可以識到新朋友仔遮😵"},{"pid":"8db98861fb595ff0aebd68271a14b80732989a1d","tid":764350,"ui